  <ThingDef ParentName="SpaceInsectThingBase">
    <defName>Cosmopillar</defName>
    <label>cosmopillar</label>
    <description>This tremendous grub holds the dubious honor of "most disgusting creature in space." Chewing through solid stone and leaving a tunnel lubricated by its own slime, the cosmopillar was originally engineered as the vanguard of a hive of asteroid-mining insects. The project has long since been abandoned, but all throughout the Rim, asteroid miners live in fear of hungry cosmopillars.\n\nRumors persist that the oldest cosmopillars enter a deep hibernation at the center of asteroids, where their unstable genetics cause them to pupate into something even more terrible...</description>
    <statBases>
      <MoveSpeed>3.60</MoveSpeed>
